Description: Multimedia player, server, encoder and transcoder
 FFmpeg is a complete, cross-platform solution to decode, encode, record,
 convert and stream audio and video.
 .
 This is a monolithic package containing all ffmpeg binaries and 
 shared libraries requried for their execution.  Installs to /opt/bci/ffmpeg.

